11#ifndef PC_STREAM_COLLECTION_H_
12#define PC_STREAM_COLLECTION_H_
13
14#include <string>
15#include <vector>
16
17#include "api/peer_connection_interface.h"
18
19namespace webrtc {
20
21// Implementation of StreamCollection.
22class StreamCollection : public StreamCollectionInterface {
23 public:
24 static rtc::scoped_refptr<StreamCollection> Create() {
25 return rtc::make_ref_counted<StreamCollection>();
26 }
27
28 static rtc::scoped_refptr<StreamCollection> Create(
29 StreamCollection* streams) {
30 return rtc::make_ref_counted<StreamCollection>(streams);
31 }
32
33 virtual size_t count() { return media_streams_.size(); }
34
35 virtual MediaStreamInterface* at(size_t index) {
36 return media_streams_.at(index);
37 }
38
39 virtual MediaStreamInterface* find(const std::string& id) {
40 for (StreamVector::iterator it = media_streams_.begin();
41 it != media_streams_.end(); ++it) {
42 if ((*it)->id().compare(id) == 0) {
43 return (*it);
44 }
45 }
46 return NULL;
47 }
48
49 virtual MediaStreamTrackInterface* FindAudioTrack(const std::string& id) {
50 for (size_t i = 0; i < media_streams_.size(); ++i) {
51 MediaStreamTrackInterface* track = media_streams_[i]->FindAudioTrack(id);
52 if (track) {
53 return track;
54 }
55 }
56 return NULL;
57 }
58
59 virtual MediaStreamTrackInterface* FindVideoTrack(const std::string& id) {
60 for (size_t i = 0; i < media_streams_.size(); ++i) {
61 MediaStreamTrackInterface* track = media_streams_[i]->FindVideoTrack(id);
62 if (track) {
63 return track;
64 }
65 }
66 return NULL;
67 }
68
69 void AddStream(MediaStreamInterface* stream) {
70 for (StreamVector::iterator it = media_streams_.begin();
71 it != media_streams_.end(); ++it) {
72 if ((*it)->id().compare(stream->id()) == 0)
73 return;
74 }
75 media_streams_.push_back(stream);
76 }
77
78 void RemoveStream(MediaStreamInterface* remove_stream) {
79 for (StreamVector::iterator it = media_streams_.begin();
80 it != media_streams_.end(); ++it) {
81 if ((*it)->id().compare(remove_stream->id()) == 0) {
82 media_streams_.erase(it);
83 break;
84 }
85 }
86 }
87
88 protected:
89 StreamCollection() {}
90 explicit StreamCollection(StreamCollection* original)
91 : media_streams_(original->media_streams_) {}
92 typedef std::vector<rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamInterface> > StreamVector;
93 StreamVector media_streams_;
94};
95
96} // namespace webrtc
97
98#endif // PC_STREAM_COLLECTION_H_
99
